               <p>Mr. Roberts. These are the duplicates I gave to the man that pawned the things.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Mrs. Gregory had these things in her hand; she gave them me to pawn. I pawned them for four shillings. I will never do the like any more.</p>
